I’m Kitty. I’m a frontend developer and engineering leader based in Berlin, with nearly 15
years of experience, primarily focused on software excellence, accessibility, diversity and
inclusion. In recent years, I have led engineering teams at [N26](https://n26.com),
[Gorillas](<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gorillas_(company)>),
[cofenster](https://cofenster.com/), and [Scilife](https://scilife.io). For a longer version, [read more
about me](/about/).
{% endrenderTemplate %}

